on the mysteries of life.

00:58:16.850 --> 00:58:18.950 align:middle line:84%
You're turning them
onto good dumplings.

00:58:18.950 --> 00:58:21.020 align:middle line:90%
Your mom's alive and well.

00:58:21.020 --> 00:58:22.400 align:middle line:90%
What are you looking toward now?

00:58:22.400 --> 00:58:26.060 align:middle line:84%
>>CHEN: I think a lot of what
I need to focus a lot of time

00:58:26.060 --> 00:58:28.820 align:middle line:90%
