Japan and exploring a lot more,

00:59:05.180 --> 00:59:08.030 align:middle line:84%
I feel like, for myself,
my own spirituality,

00:59:08.030 --> 00:59:10.430 align:middle line:90%
get myself more grounded.

00:59:10.430 --> 00:59:14.030 align:middle line:84%
I think that's the
most important thing.

00:59:14.030 --> 00:59:17.100 align:middle line:84%
I don't see myself as
a popular anything.

00:59:17.100 --> 00:59:17.900 align:middle line:90%
I just see myself--

00:59:17.900 --> 00:59:18.830 align:middle line:84%
I'm doing what I'm
passionate about.

00:59:18.830 --> 00:59:19.910 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: You're just doing
what you love right now.

00:59:19.910 --> 00:59:20.210 align:middle line:90%
>>CHEN: Yeah.

00:59:20.210 --> 00:59:22.370 align:middle line:84%
And then I'm fortunate
enough that people

00:59:22.370 --> 00:59:24.240 align:middle line:90%
