the best version of myself

00:59:29.180 --> 00:59:29.980 align:middle line:90%
to everybody.

00:59:29.980 --> 00:59:32.240 align:middle line:84%
Because if I lose that,
then that's everything.

00:59:32.240 --> 00:59:33.900 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So you're going to
take a little inside time.

00:59:33.900 --> 00:59:34.370 align:middle line:90%
>>CHEN: Take some time.

