countries in the last year

00:59:36.380 --> 00:59:37.880 align:middle line:84%
traveling eight
months of last year?

00:59:37.880 --> 00:59:41.070 align:middle line:84%
>>CHEN: Last year, I was
in about 15 countries.

00:59:41.070 --> 00:59:41.870 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:59:41.870 --> 00:59:43.328 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Eight
months on the road.

